<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #3B82F6; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #3B82F6; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 10px 5px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ“‹ New Document Review Required</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi <%= @review.reviewer.first_name %>,</h2>
      
      <p>A new business registration document requires your review and approval.</p>
      
      <p><strong>Registration Details:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Business Name: <%= @registration.business_name %></li>
        <li>Business Type: <%= @registration.business_category.name %></li>
        <li>State: <%= @registration.state.name %></li>
        <li>Applicant: <%= @registration.user.full_name %></li>
        <li>Submitted: <%= @registration.created_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Please review the documents and either approve or request changes.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= @review_url %>" class="button">Review Documents</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>